description:
76 Action-Packed Arachnid-Pages!

Agent Venom is back and he's waging a one-symbiote war on crime! But is he prepared for the Superior Spider-Man?!

Plus, it's a battle royale between the Masters of Evil and the Superior Six!

Also, In the aftermath of Kraven’s hunt, will all of Scarlet Spider’s friends abandon him… or betray him?!!

Includes material reprinted from Superior Spider-Man #22, Superior Spider-Man Team-Up #6, Scarlet Spider Vol.2 #24!

76 Action-Packed Arachnid-Pages!

Agent Venom is the prisoner of the Superior Spider-Man!

Plus, Spider-Man is at the mercy of the Superior Six!

Also, Scarlet Spider has survived everything that has been thrown at him, from the Assassin’s Guild to Kraven the Hunter! But will he survive the return of Shathra?!!

Includes material reprinted from Superior Spider-Man #23, Superior Spider-Man Team-Up #7, Scarlet Spider Vol.2 #25!

76 Action-Packed Arachnid-Pages!

The Venom symbiote has taken over the Superior Spider-Man. Now, brace yourselves for the Superior Venom!

Plus: Namor is being hunted by the Black Panther's assassins! Only the Superior Spider-Man can save him!

Also: Brace yourselves for Boomerang, Beetle, Shocker, Speed-Demon and Overdrive, the All-New Sinister Six (Yes, we know that’s only five)!

Includes material reprinted from Superior Spider-Man #24, Superior Spider-Man Team-Up #8, Superior Foes of Spider-Man #1!

76 Action-Packed Arachnid-Pages!

The Superior Venom versus The Avengers! This time it’s war!

Plus: The Superior Spider-Man’s war on crime draws the attention of Daredevil and Punisher! But are they friend or foe?!!

Also: Will the Sinister Six survive an attack by Punisher?!!

Includes material reprinted from Superior Spider-Man #25, Superior Spider-Man Team-Up #9, Superior Foes of Spider-Man #2!

76 Action-Packed Arachnid-Pages!

The countdown to ‘Goblin Nation’ begins! The Green Goblin vs. Hobgoblin! The final battle!

Plus: Spider-Man has been betrayed by his own minions! Can the Web-Slinger, Daredevil and Punisher and survive against the Spider-lings!

Also: The Sinister Six embark on the quest for the head of Silvermane?!!

Includes material reprinted from Superior Spider-Man #26, The Superior Foes of Spider-Man #3!

76 Action-Packed Arachnid-Pages!

‘Goblin Nation’ begins! Is it the beginning of the end for the Superior Spider-Man? Otto Octavius's dreams of being the Superior Spider-Man are going up in flames as the Goblin King takes over New York!

Plus: Doctor Octopus versus Green Goblin! ‘Nuff said!

Also: The Sinister Six are attacked by Power Man and Iron Fist!

Includes material reprinted from Superior Spider-Man #27, Superior Spider-Man Team-Up #11, Superior Foes of Spider-Man #4!

76 Action-Packed Arachnid-Pages!

‘Goblin Nation’ continues! Spider-Island burns as the Goblin King brings the Superior Spider-Man's kingdom crashing down!

Plus: Spider-Man faces a new crisis when the Inhuman city Attilan falls… New York!

Also: In their quest for the head of Silvermane, the Sinister Six are going to rob the merciless crime boss known as The Owl!

Includes material reprinted from Superior Spider-Man #28, Inhumanity Superior Spider-Man #1, Superior Foes of Spider-Man #5!

76 Action-Packed Arachnid-Pages!

Goblin Nation reaches its climatic conclusion!

This is it! This is the moment the last 32 issues have been building to! Peter Parker is back! Now he must take down the Goblin King and his Goblin Nation!

Plus, the secret war between Doctor Octopus and the Green Goblin is revealed!

Includes material reprinted from Superior Spider-Man #31 and Superior Spider-Man Team-Up #12!

100-Page Action-Packed Arachnid-Special!

Peter Parker is back as the one-and-only Spider-Man! Not only does he have to contend with foes old and new, but he also has to rebuild his life and the legacy of Doc Ock actions as the Superior Spider-Man!

Plus, a dimension-hopping epic begins, as the Spider-Men from two dimensions meet!

Also, Bullseye, the world’s deadliest assassin, versus Boomerang, the world’s worst villain!

Includes material reprinted from Amazing Spider-Man #1, Spider-Men #1-2, Superior Foes of Spider-Man #9!

76 pages of Earth's Mightiest Heroes!

The Mighty Avengers are reborn! Luke Cage assembles a new team when New York is invaded by alien killers! Don't miss a new chapter of Avengers history by Al Ewing and Greg Land!

The Uncanny Avengers face the wrath of the Celestials - the creators of humanity have returned! By Rick Remender and Daniel Acuna!

Featuring material first printed in Mighty Avengers #1-2 and Uncanny Avengers #7.

76 pages of Earth's Mightiest Heroes!

The Mighty Avengers battle the monstrous Shuma-Gorath, the dark god from another dimension! By Al Ewing and Greg Land!

Captain America learns Wolverine's most shameful secret – and throws him out of the Uncanny Avengers! By Rick Remender and Daniel Acuna!

Featuring material first published in Mighty Avengers #3 and Uncanny Avengers #8-9.

100-PAGE SPECIAL!

More action from Earth's Mightiest Heroes!

The Young Avengers are back, and Loki is pulling their strings! Don't miss the start of a hot new story by Kieron Gillen and Jamie McKelvie!

The Uncanny Avengers clash with the Four Horsemen of Apocalypse! By Rick Remender and Daniel Acuna!

The Mighty Avengers face a leadership challenge from the Superior Spider-Man!

Featuring material first published in Young Avengers #1-2, Uncanny Avengers #10-11 and Mighty Avengers #4.

76 pages of Earth's Mightiest Heroes!

The Four Horsemen are back from the dead! Banshee, Daken, the Grim Reaper and the Sentry attack the Uncanny Avengers! by Rick Remender and Daniel Acuna!

The Superior Spider-Man challenges Luke Cage for leadership of the Mighty Avengers! By Al Ewing and Greg Land!

The Young Avengers and Loki confront a monstrous extra-dimensional threat! By Kieron Gillen and Jamie McKelvie!

Featuring material first published in Uncanny Avengers #11-12, Mighty Avengers #5 and Young Avengers #3.

76 pages of Earth's Mightiest Heroes!

The Uncanny Avengers battle the Four Horsemen of Apocalypse – and one of them is Wolverine's dead son Daken! By Rick Remender and Daniel Acuna!

The Black Widow, Spider-Woman and Hawkeye fight to survive in Russia! By Kelly Sue DeConnick and Pete Woods!

The Young Avengers are on the run, battling the most dangerous enemies of all – their own parents! By Kieron Gillen and Jamie McKelvie!

Featuring material first published in Uncanny Avengers #13, Avengers Assemble #12 and Young Avengers #4.

The Music Issue

Feel the beatz with Cadence and Dubstep Puffle in our music special! Party and solve puzzles with the Penguin Band, read our latest comic strip starring Rookie, Gary and Jet Pack Guy, and check out your latest igloos and fashions!

Every reader gets a trio of musical items for their penguin, 1500 coins and a cool gift! So get ready to rock!

The Holiday Issue

Pack your bags, 'cos CP mag is going on holiday! Solve puzzles on Rockhopper's Grand Cruise, go wild at the CP Summer Camp with your penguin pals, and discover the secret story of Jet Pack Guy! And would you like your very own squid in a bottle? Head over to Gary's new experiments page and get creative!

What's more, every reader gets a FREE Puffle Catch game, exclusive beach items, 1,500 coins, and best of all... A FREE 1 MONTH MEMBERSHIP! So waddle on down to your local newsagent today.

The Secret Agent Issue

Are you tough enough for advanced EPF agent training? Join Agent G, Rookie and Jet Pack Guy and solve the challenges to become an advanced secret agent! Work on your Jet Pack skills, train Elite Puffles with PH and turn your iggy into a Mission HQ with FREE spy items for every reader!

What’s more, you get a FREE water soaker and two button badges, plus 1500 coins!

Class of 2014 Special!

Club Penguin Mag is too cool for school with our Class of 2014 special!

Prove your knowledge in the ultimate CP quiz, host your perfect prom party, and get to know CP's latest monster, the Megalodon!

What's more, every reader gets a FREE globe, desk and chair for their iggy, a cool puffle stationery set, a treasure book item AND 1500 coins!

So what are you waiting for? Get to class!

Christmas Countdown Issue!

Ho-ho-hello and welcome to our fun-filled Christmas countdown issue! We're ticking off the days until Christmas with pages of festive fun, including a Cadence comic surprise, Herbert puzzles, and instructions on how to make your own puffle Christmas tree decorations!

What's more, every reader gets 4 free Christmas items and a packet of popping puffles! So waddle down to your local newsagent or supermarket today!
